  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Select between one of the following designations:</p><ul><li><em><strong>B:</strong></em> When you would successfully land a weapon attack, you gain a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls against the creature you hit until the end of the current turn. This can stack up to three times.</li><li><em><strong>S:</strong></em> You do not need to roll concentration checks when maintaining jutsu with the Sensory keyword, and allied creatures other than yourself gain a bonus +1d4 to attack and damage rolls against creatures within 60 feet of you.</li></ul>",
